+
+- [Alpine Linux CVE Tracker](https://security.alpinelinux.org)  
+- [MIT Kerberos Project](https://web.mit.edu/kerberos/)  
+- [CVE Record – CVE-2000-0546](https://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2000-0546)
